				<td colspan="2"><span>What me die??   Never....
<br />

<br />
/secretly send tells to uber_cleric_01 , &quot;i have 6 corpse in pod graveyard mind dropping by and rezzing them,  please!!! /beg&quot;
<br />

<br />
I found that the flies are the hardest to swarm with..   because you would have to worry about that Malarian thing thats near by...  get too near to it.. and it'll join your swarm.. and either summon you.. or dot you death.  (mmm.. maybe thats deeper in the zone)
<br />

<br />
Anyways, I found an easier place to swarm,  head over to the CCY (infront of that bone wall)  theres that wide open spot there nice place to kite.. no objects to run into lots of room to circle.  head straight out from that spot..  and go out to the end of the spit there, circle back.... to the open spot..   and watch all the goos and rats all make thier way to you .. (Panic <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />  kidding of course)  get into 3rd person view.. and make your large circle run around the open area.   get all your adds together and start charming..<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />    You don't even have to worry about lev here.
<br />

<br />
ohh.. side note..  if your out of mana..  run into your swarm accidentally on purpose.  take pictures... come back loot your corpse except for that one item,  and start again with full mana bar....
<br />

<br />
pay uber cleric later, for rezes later..
<br />
</span></td>
